Full Description: With a combined 25 years of business experience amongst our management team, we are ready to tackle any challenge and put our clients on the path to success they are looking for. Driving sales and having a low ROI allows for our clients to trust that The Connecticut Team has the client and consumers' best interest in mind. For us, there is no one for the other. Our blended model of traditional and innovative marketing and sales services has enabled us to surpass our competitors in the markets we are in. Over the past decade, especially more recently with the pandemic, it has become increasingly difficult to make a personalized experience for the average consumer or the average employee. We have invested our time to figure out how to create a genuinely personal experience for them. For our clients, we offer direct, in-person consultations and are able to tailor each conversation and sales presentation to the prospective client. This not only drives revenue but creates long-term brand loyalty. Our brand of marketing takes customer service to the next level. The main focus is to “wow” our customers and clients. By emphasizing quality acquisitions and exceptional training, we have been able to expand our customer base for our campaigns by thousands. We focus on finding out what each customer truly needs to preserve the reputation of our clients and ensure long-term sustainable growth. Other services we offer include but are not limited to rapid expansion plans, strategic territory management, top-notch brand representatives, hands-on or hands-off sales processing depending on the client's needs.  To sum it up, speed to market and low overhead. Our clients pay based on results and we are able to in turn pay our employees competitively due to our low overhead. To find out how The Connecticut Team can directly impact your brand, contact us connect@theconncecticutteam.com

Full Description: A TOP-NOTCH LEGAL TEAM WITH A PERSONAL APPROACH At Denton Peterson, our attorneys have been serving clients since 1995 in the greater Phoenix area. We offer top-quality legal work without the bureaucracy and higher costs of larger law firms. All our attorneys have worked at large law firms in Arizona. Now, in a smaller environment, we offer a more personal and responsive approach for each of our client’s needs. Areas Of Practice - Business And Corporate Law - Employment Law - Litigation/Appellate Practice - Franchising Law - Collections Lawyers - Real Estate Matters At Denton Peterson our first priority is your success. We help with contracts. You may need different types of contracts in your business. As an employer, you will want to know your options related to non-compete agreements, and many businesses will also need a non-disclosure agreement (NDA) to use when revealing confidential company information or entering into sensitive negotiations.
